{"tid":1503633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求每次行動﹕要諗定plan A / B / C","createTime":"2019-08-25T04:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T05:39:07.000Z","uid":2719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ceb774beb4d53eb546afa75469eae47ffd1b6d0","tid":1503633,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"Plan A : 黨鐵封幾個站<br />\n我地就去B<br />\n<br />\nPlan B﹕黨鐵又封幾個站<br />\n我地就去C<br />\n<br />\nPlan C﹕有本事再封幾個站<br />\n我地就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遍地開花</span><br />\n<br />\n每個遊行點嘅站封曬，間接幫我地塞路。<br />\n我地再遍地開花，一舉兩得。<br />\n同埋自己區玩全部都係街坊，走都易啲。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話有plan B就夠，封得一個遊行點，<br />\n封埋另一個有幾難決定，但封三個就夠癱瘓黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n大家要有共識，如果3個PLAN都無封站，<br />\n唔好揀去離自己近啲嘅B/C，都係去A。<br />\n封A去B封B去C咁排落去，唔係人數就會分散。<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048a0cd7d3ca9d005d807a3770256ec0c6b72d20","tid":1503633,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a79174389010810150e6084df41aa145e652bea9","tid":1503633,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ded87ef41ee66f9c5d0c961ddc53cad74422929e","tid":1503633,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88852eb4b9dccc0e4827ec67454adb0b6074a32d","tid":1503633,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: